# English-only (Tippon)

**Disclaimer:** Everything related to this project—**user-visible strings**, **developer-facing comments**, **commit messages**, **alerts**, **tooltips**, **error messages**, **agent/Composer instructions in-repo**, and **documentation meant for maintainers**—must be written in **English**.

- Do not introduce Spanish or other languages in the codebase unless explicitly requested for a localized feature (i18n), which this project does not use by default.
- Existing Spanish in legacy files should be migrated to English when touched.
- Config/docs pairing (`CONFIG_PROTOCOL_README.md` / `CLAUDE.md`) remains in English.
